Quickstrike:




Quickstrike suddenly went silent. He faintly heard the screaming of a 
female. He thought it was Mantella, but it wasn't the right tone. He 
listened in, and finally decided to search it out.

"Be right back boss," he said to Megatron. He took a step to the side. "If 
ya need me right quick, jus' give me uh holler." After that he walked out of 
the room. Once he made a few steps into the hallway, he went into a jog, 
following the sound. He was a little worried of what he would find.

He skidded off to a turn to the right, and followed from there. After a few 
seconds, he came across an open room, where he thought where the origins of 
the screams where.

He entered the threshold of the room, seeing a female bot straped to a table 
and Black Arachnia standing near-by.

The only thing that came out was: "What in tarnation?"
